## 2026 AI Agent Implementation Constraints

### Stack (NEVER deviate)
- FastAPI + PydanticAI + LangGraph ONLY
- NEVER use LangChain standard agent wrappers (initialize_agent, create_react_agent)
- Database: asyncpg with raw SQL. NO SQLAlchemy or any ORM.
- Package manager: uv ONLY

### Agent boundaries
- Agents MUST NOT communicate directly with each other
- MasterOrchestrator is the ONLY node that mutates routing_target in shared state
- Every agent output MUST validate against a predefined Pydantic schema
- Unstructured text output from an agent = failure

### Tools
- Tools MUST NEVER throw raw Python exceptions to the execution loop
- Every tool wraps exceptions and returns ToolResult schema with error_message + can_retry bool
- Max 2 retries per tool call, each logged separately

### Code generation rules
- Define Pydantic schema BEFORE writing any functional logic
- Use raw asyncpg for all DB calls — no ORMs
- git commit before any multi-file refactoring